You can use nix to setup all dependencies (without nvim)
look shell.nix as example

or you need ghc, stack, haskell-language-server, fast-tags, hoogle

# change NVIM_DATA_MINIMAL to fixed folder
alias haskell-ide='NVIM_DATA_MINIMAL="/tmp/minimal" NVIM_APP_NAME="nvim-ht-minimal" nvim -u minimal.lua Main.hs'
